body:
I'm hitting the same problem. Using `optimization.sideEffects: false` seems to work around the issue for me.
I'm using:

```js
optimization: {
	splitChunks: {
		cacheGroups: {
			commons: {
				test: /\.(js|jsx|ts|tsx)$/i,
				name: 'vendors',
				chunks: 'all',
				minChunks: 10,
			}
		}
	}
}
```
